"replyTime":"2020-10-30T17:38:58.000Z","msg":"我地只要食多d黃店 打Twitter 戰線<br />\n就可以努力返工 安坐家中光復到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算手足上庭我地都有旁聽師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以手足方面唔需要擔心 佢地唔孤獨<br />\n我建議香港人課金比david 幫我地抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續推12手足po推到佢地見到為止就贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我好撚鍾意香港 <br />\n今生只嫁前線巴 <br />\n博盡無悔<br />\n不自由 毋寧死"}]}